{"tid":2315280,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"假設你留係香港，21 歲時:","createTime":"2020-12-07T05:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T06:41:30.000Z","uid":36383,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"12868c7f9a3fb147ec70eb65d5ccda6a74388707","tid":2315280,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:55:21.000Z","msg":"假設你留咗係香港: <br />\n<br />\n入讀香港臭名昭著嘅香港大學, BBA <br />\n<br />\n21 歲時: 畢業前完成咗 4 份 internship, 拎咗 5 個 scholarship, 拎咗靚 MT offer ，一畢業就平步青雲，漸入佳境。每個月請完港女女朋友食飯，仲夠錢課金 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為香港炒股唔洗交 capital gain tax ，好快你意外有筆橫財，身家過百萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n31 歲時: 9成按買咗層居屋，原來仲有錢剩去擺酒同渡蜜月。因為移民潮，公司打算升你做 department head 。工餘時間你已經學到法文 C2 level ，考埋紅酒牌，開口 bonjour 埋口 carrefour，靜靜回想起結婚時播嘅 marriage de amour<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n41 歲時: 開始煩啲仔女嘢，決定送個仔去國際學校然後大個用 Bno visa 同太空人計劃送出英國讀書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又差唔多踏入公司權力核心，你讀咗個 LLM 準備用中國式法律管公司下屬。返工挑逗少女MT，收工玩弄熟女老婆。每日收工達成 work life balance ，然後去附近一間法式餐廳，叫咗條 boudin blanc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n51 歲時: 五十而知天命，你成立咗間海外空殼公司 ，又係香港開咗間自己嘅公司，個名都算係 CEO <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同時你發現銀行戶口啲錢有點滿，於時補地價，然後居屋放租，自己則換間村屋，買部波子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你發誓都估唔到，當日 2020 年打算移民英國嘅中學同學會係一條小租租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為資金耗盡佢不得不返香港<br />\n<br />\n61 歲時: 花甲之年嘅你，因為 Bno visa 早已係 BC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係你所憧憬嘅並非 London 嘅帶雨嘅陰天，也非 Boston 般嘅美式生活。你開始回憶起當年 21 歲移民潮時，被世人遺忘，位於法國東南部嘅 Lyon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 憑住你現有嘅資產，同埋 C2 嘅法文水平，2年後你變賣一切，係法國重新生活<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n而你嘅細女就入讀當地住名嘅 ecole polytechnique，自豪享有真正嘅 X life，相反你舊同學嘅仔女只係讀緊可憐嘅 Hong kong polytechnique ，只有不斷 chur intern project 嘅 u life <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n81歲時: 你回顧人生，沒有一點遺憾"},{"pid":"a518e4327d92db90f810aa673bb624147d955975","tid":2315280,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好再問樓主係邊 thx"},{"pid":"2aa861d9a2aa4d09f131f537fcbf9b5cb836419d","tid":2315280,"uid":324018,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"d錢一早比人充公左，31歲時：完"},{"pid":"9aab5a901f2deabd2ad4468f803b02d3ee45310e","tid":2315280,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2aa861d9a2aa4d09f131f537fcbf9b5cb836419d","tid":2315280,"uid":324018,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"d錢一早比人充公左，31歲時：完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 31 歲時已有離岸戶口，充公只係提早起程"},{"pid":"64f0301496376748226cdaf073e956ac34862d4f","tid":2315280,"uid":205191,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a518e4327d92db90f810aa673bb624147d955975","tid":2315280,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好再問樓主係邊 thx"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:41:04.000Z","msg":"本hr<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea1c66f424e178f39054cdd0567be0f15daef0d","tid":2315280,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"64f0301496376748226cdaf073e956ac34862d4f","tid":2315280,"uid":205191,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a518e4327d92db90f810aa673bb624147d955975","tid":2315280,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好再問樓主係邊 thx"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:41: